      <title>随着新加坡金融管理局的政策转向成为焦点，新加坡元势将走弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/singapore-dollar-set-to-weaken-as-mas-pivot-comes-into-focus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在市场预期新加坡央行将转向宽松政策且美国关税将波及全球经济的背景下，新加坡货币疲软的局面可能将持续下去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/singapore-dollar-set-to-weaken-as-mas-pivot-comes-into-focus</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
